WEBVTT

00:03:29.136 --> 00:03:33.396
baada ya ugonjwa kumweka shambani mwake
Georgia kwa miaka kumi na mbili.

00:03:33.556 --> 00:03:35.036
Kwenye miaka hiyo,

00:03:35.036 --> 00:03:37.316
aliandika kazi zake nyingi
alizokuwa akiwaza.

00:03:37.416 --> 00:03:40.246
Uwezo wake wa kuhama kati ya
maudhi na uvumbuzi

00:03:40.376 --> 00:03:44.536
unaendelea kuvutia wasomaji kwenye
dunia yake ya kufikirika isiyoisha.

00:03:44.696 --> 00:03:47.176
Kama mhusika Tom Shirlet anavyosema,

00:03:47.436 --> 00:03:49.316
mwili ni "kama nyumba:

00:03:49.416 --> 00:03:50.696
haiendi popote,

00:03:50.766 --> 00:03:53.750
lakini roho, mwanamke,
ni kama gari moto:

00:03:53.880 --> 00:03:56.150
daima lipo kwenye mwendo".